name: Hollow Pixels 4 - Pat
description:
One might be frightened by some of those creatures: You need not worry, as they are only pixels, which won’t come out of the screen.
 But one must be wary of what they might summon from the depth of our psyché. 
This one for example is often referred to as « Pat », as it can trigger memories of a famous sponge’s sidekick. Others might trigger less fortunate associations.

IG&Twitter:  @dacosta_works
